{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4a377e7084","title":"七十五岁居民恳求“退休”的报告","origin":"拓荒者据原件录入、提供。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ab12b39478","index":0,"year":1971,"month":6,"day":4,"articleId":"4a377e7084"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1bef196bab","name":"刘富贵（化名）"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e014d118b3","type":"title","text":"七十五岁居民恳求“退休”的报告","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"},{"id":"981eb4e015","type":"authors","text":"刘富贵（化名）","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"},{"id":"8a77a5258c","type":"subtitle","text":"〖刘富贵，湖南城镇居民。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"},{"id":"f34fc048a7","type":"appellation","text":"吕仙亭居委会负责同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"},{"id":"2436009a15","type":"paragraph","text":"六九年九月十八号起，挖防空洞到十二月廿号，共计拾伍个半工。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"},{"id":"48743d1724","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月廿号，奉命到五里公社修路，到廿六号，白天五个工，又做晚工两个，半夜一点起到早晨六点钟收工回来。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"},{"id":"a54dda57b6","type":"paragraph","text":"七零年元月初四起，到大桥湖中桥没罗【灭螺】，七天之久完成任务回家。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"},{"id":"a185863a91","type":"paragraph","text":"到三月奉命拾砖碴子两天，第一天九担，第二天拾担。又到五里公社修补路二天，在广场挖沟（子）一天。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"},{"id":"0bf953d0c7","type":"paragraph","text":"又到七〇年，挖防空洞前后五个半工。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"},{"id":"350053e1db","type":"paragraph","text":"团   到五月一号、三号两天办地种棉花。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"},{"id":"b00452bca9","type":"paragraph","text":"又到五月十五号锄棉花三天，五月廿四号锄棉花三天。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"},{"id":"101595e9cb","type":"paragraph","text":"到五月廿六摘桑叶半天，到六月二号摘桑叶一天。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"},{"id":"83b20f3986","type":"paragraph","text":"此【本】人年龄七十五岁了，应该退休了，政府照顾。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"},{"id":"2d846053e7","type":"paragraph","text":" 居民刘富贵 71年六月4 号","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084"}],"page":{"id":"a33b736c38","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4a377e7084","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}